a major pain point for me has been the getUpcomingSong() is very unrelieant, sometimes it gives the correct songs, often time it fails. Mostly because YT Music shows differnent type of queues for different actions.
I am attaching some example images
Note that one thing that is common is that the currently playing song always has someoverlay on top of the album art, and we should go and pick the next item from the list as the upcoming song, this will require use to jump over "autoplay" box and I am also attaching HTML element of different kind of queue.
can you work on fixing this problem?
